history.content:
Welcome back, bears! We're so excited to kickstart the fall semester with our SWElcome Week events starting today! We can't wait to meet you all and see you all again!

Our RSVP form is closed, but feel free to attend! You may not be able to get food, but we would still love to meet you! Here is the schedule of all the events for Welcome Week and the links for our virtual events!

9/8 6-7pm PT – [VIRTUAL] Game Night on Zoom

Description: We're so excited to kick off our welcome week with our Game Night! Grab your favorite snacks and join us for a chance to meet some amazing women in STEM while competing in some fun online games. We can't wait to meet you and see you all again! 

Link:https://berkeley.zoom.us/j/94231439788?pwd=RzhZcWpNNWtxRGFpemsvR3Q5UnlSQT09

9/9 6-7:30pm PT( not 6-7pm anymore)– [HYBRID] General Meeting #1

Description: Join us at SWE’s first general meeting of the semester. Come find out how you can become involved in SWE this virtual semester and how you can join a committee! We are so excited to have you!

Location: 290 Hearst Memorial Mining Building (HMMB) or register here for the zoom link

 

9/10 5-7:30pm PT – [IN-PERSON] Bechtel Terrace Picnic

Description: Close out your busy week and hang out with us at Bechtel Terrace! We'll be having a relaxing picnic with snacks, ice cream, and good vibes! Treat yourself! Hope to see you there!

Location: Bechtel Terrace
history.subject: Come out to SWElcome Week!!!
